Package xsystem.enums

xsystem.enums is a group of classes for character representation in strings and XStructures
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CharClass
    Represents the class of character in string.
    XClass
    Represents the class of character in XStructures.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LCC
    Represents LowerCase Characters in a string.
    NUM
    Represents Numeral Characters in string.
    SPC
    Represents Special Characters in string.
    UCC
    Represents UpperCase Characters in string.
    X_ANY
    Represents Any Character in a XStructure.
    X_LCC
    Represents LowerCase Character in a XStructure.
    X_NUM
    Represents Numeral Character in a XStructure.
    X_OR
    Represents a List of most seen character in a XStructure.
    X_SPEC
    Represents Special Character in a XStructure.
    X_UCC
    Represents UpperCase Character in a XStructure.
